\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2 \cf3 \super 3\'a0
\f4\b0 \nosupersub Then Peter said, \'93Ananias, how is it that Satan\'a0has so filled your heart\'a0that you have lied to the Holy Spirit\'a0and have kept for yourself some of the money you received for the land?\'a0
\f2\b \super 4\'a0
\f4\b0 \nosupersub Didn\'92t it belong to you before it was sold? And after it was sold, wasn\'92t the money at your disposal?\'a0What made you think of doing such a thing? You have not lied just to human beings but to God.\'94  Acts 5\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Peter says that Ananias lies to both the Spirit and then God\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He uses those two names interchangeably.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is not wrong to lie to an object or force\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
