{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Acts 16:6 \'96 If Paul only used the Bible as a guide he would have went to the wrong place\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa240\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
